race.comment: PHANTOM'S CHASE (3) peaks off two solid middle-distance placings in provincial grade. He positions forward and is well-placed to break through. HONEYJOY (6) rates similarly off her two placings and there was little in it the latest at Hamilton over this distance. Maps for the run of the race and she's a threat. STREAMELOT (9) didn't get into in last time in a CL1 in South Australia, but her effort at Ballarat prior stacks up. Jumps from a soft gate and has each-way claims. Ditto CONJURER (2), who was only beaten 2.6L in the same Ballarat contest. Made good improvement and he's likely to race forward and get every chance.
